{"title":"数据库代码语法","slug":"数据库代码语法","date":"2020-10-28T05:59:08.000Z","updated":"2020-12-12T06:40:18.218Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/数据库代码语法.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"登录数据库1<br>myaql -u root -proot;<br>","covers":null,"content":"<h5 id=\"登录数据库\"><a href=\"#登录数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"登录数据库\"></a>登录数据库</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">myaql -u root -proot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h5 id=\"创建数据表库\"><a href=\"#创建数据表库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建数据表库\"></a>创建数据表库</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create database 库名;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"创建数据表表\"><a href=\"#创建数据表表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建数据表表\"></a>创建数据表表</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create table user</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name char(4),</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tel int,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    content int,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    date VARCHAR(20)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)ENGINE&#x3D;MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET&#x3D;gb2312;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"查看数据表\"><a href=\"#查看数据表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看数据表\"></a>查看数据表</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">show databases;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"查看表的数据\"><a href=\"#查看表的数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看表的数据\"></a>查看表的数据</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">desc 表名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"添加数据代码\"><a href=\"#添加数据代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加数据代码\"></a>添加数据代码</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">insert into user(uid,sname,email,tnum,score)</span><br><span class=\"line\">values(&#39;123456&#39;,&#39;qert&#39;,&#39;123123@qq.com&#39;,&#39;1456789&#39;,&#39;100&#39;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"查看表格内容\"><a href=\"#查看表格内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看表格内容\"></a>查看表格内容</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select *</span><br><span class=\"line\">from 表名;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"中文\"><a href=\"#中文\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"中文\"></a>中文</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">set names gbk;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"修改表内的数据\"><a href=\"#修改表内的数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改表内的数据\"></a>修改表内的数据</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">update 表名</span><br><span class=\"line\">set orededate &#x3D; &#39;2016-10-01&#39; 要改的数据 </span><br><span class=\"line\">where bid&#x3D;&#39;3&#39;and uid&#x3D;&#39;1003&#39; 条件</span><br><span class=\"line\">先数据后条件 不然就出错</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"备份及还原数据库\"><a href=\"#备份及还原数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"备份及还原数据库\"></a>备份及还原数据库</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- 备份</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysqldump -uroot -hlocalhost --default-character-set&#x3D;gbk -p123456 网上书店&gt;D:&#x2F;bak&#x2F;网上书店_2001.sql</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 还原</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql -uroot -p 网上书店&lt;D:&#x2F;bak&#x2F;网上书店_2001.sql</span><br><span class=\"line\">drop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"获取今天的年份\"><a href=\"#获取今天的年份\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"获取今天的年份\"></a>获取今天的年份</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT YEAR(NOW());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"查询日期之显示年份\"><a href=\"#查询日期之显示年份\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查询日期之显示年份\"></a>查询日期之显示年份</h5><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT YEAR(orderdate)</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM b_order</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[],"tags":[]}